  "prompt": "Who are some of the best lawyers in India?",
  "response": "India has numerous highly esteemed lawyers who have made significant contributions to the legal field. Some of the notable ones include:\n\n1. **Harish Salve**: Renowned for his expertise in constitutional, commercial, and international law. He has represented India in international forums and has handled some high-profile cases.\n\n2. **Fali S. Nariman**: A senior advocate who has played a pivotal role in shaping Indian jurisprudence. He is well-regarded for his work in constitutional law and has won several accolades for his contributions.\n\n3. **Ram Jethmalani**: Known for his sharp legal acumen and bold courtroom tactics, he has handled many landmark cases throughout his career.\n\n4. **Kapil Sibal**: A prominent lawyer and politician, he has served as Union Minister and has a strong background in constitutional and administrative law.\n\n5. **Gopal Subramanium**: Former Solicitor General of India, he has a rich experience in various fields of law, including constitutional, civil, and criminal law.\n\n6. **Abhishek Manu Singhvi**: A senior advocate and politician, he has a strong reputation in constitutional and corporate law.\n\n7. **Mukul Rohatgi**: Former Attorney General of India, known for his expertise in constitutional and corporate law.\n\nThese individuals are recognized for their exceptional legal skills, significant contributions to the field, and their roles in high-stakes cases.",
